text: Lypsimena nodipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hermann Burmeister in 1865. It is known from Argentina, Uruguay and Brazil.BioLib.cz - Lypsimena nodipennis. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1865
